features: 【🦖Dinosaur Design🦖】Our car toys are designed to a dinosaur shaped. There is a cool cartoon pterosaur doll, removable, and the car is equipped with music and LED lights. Bringing more joy to boys who love rc car toys.
【👦Designed for Little Boys👦】Simple operation, just two buttons can control unicorn car forward, backward and turn. One click control for music playback/pause, lights on when the power is on.

【📡Signal Strengthening📡】 Remote control car and Controller strengthen the signal antenna, the longest operating distance can reach 5 meters. Using 2.4Ghz frequency, fast response, no interference, allowing multiple car to play at the same time.

【⚒Durable & Safe and Non-toxic🍃 】Dinosaur RC Car use sleek design to avoid scratches. The interior of the car is reinforced with a bracket to ensure that car can withstand bumps and collisions. Each component is made of non-toxic ABS plastic and has no small parts that are easy to swallow.
【🎁Best Gift🎁】Unique Dinosaur Design, Exquisite packaging, Sturdy and Durable, Simple operation. Our Remote Control Car is the best holiday, carnival, and birthday gift for 2 3 4 5 year old boys.

【🔋 Rechargeable Battery 🔋】 Our dino remote control car is equipped with a rechargeable battery that only takes 30 minutes to charge, can play for 2.5 hours, and is equipped with a charging cable in the box. Note: Remote control requires 2 AAA batteries, not included.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Dino RC car
reviews.reviewText: My grandson is 3 years old, he really likes this dino car. It's easy to play, the car can move forward and backward with just two buttons. Its quality is also good, no need to worry about damage. What surprised me was that the car is equipped with music and light, it looks very cool!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: My one year old absolutely adores this little car !!!! The lights aren't to bright but enough to get his attention. The music isn't too loud and he likes that as well . Also the remote is very easy for him to use . I'd definitely recommend this one as a first remote control car !

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for little ones
reviews.reviewText: This toy is so well-made, and so adorable, first of all, I love the fact that the car part is chargeable, the handheld remote does require batteries, but that’s fine, it has three buttons, one for one for backward, and one for music, the cute little thing lights up, I love it. Absolutely adorable, cute gift.
